{"tid":247524,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係英國讀書，黎緊會去grad trip，但好驚","createTime":"2017-05-18T00:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T07:32:20.000Z","uid":107043,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25aa45bc3eef68f15c1a20c5e4e87b446fa72e09","tid":247524,"uid":107043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"黎緊6左右就會去grad trip, 都會去好幾個國家，包括摩洛哥，奧地利，克羅地亞，希臘，荷蘭，西班牙等<br />\n本應係一個好開心既grad trip, 但係我哩排就不段係度亂稔野，好驚去旅行時發生意外，好似會遇到恐襲交通意外。 <br />\n講真財物損失我唔介意，我最怕就係身體上既損傷。<br />\n依家咁驚可能因為好期待遲啲9月有得返香港繼續升學， 好怕遇到意外就享受唔到係香港嘅大學生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉屌，我真係好撚廢咁都驚一餐，有冇巴絲可以開解一下我，又或者有冇一啲關於恐怖襲擊情報嘅網站比我睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fadd3b90987e4eee7455a011c27192b4e80ba5","tid":247524,"uid":114147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"我都英國grad 6月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n上年3月係 germany 俾人偷左 400 euro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb341436566f3e4fab4c93611f9c110b9a46a2e","tid":247524,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"係你就係你，驚嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\n英國都有機會恐怖襲擊，周街都有車<br />\n香港都有支那迷暈黨，更多亂渣車嘅司機"},{"pid":"44a17293c0c0e26c28394e19857c79015e761ee0","tid":247524,"uid":3223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都英國grad 6月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n上年3月係 germany 俾人偷左 400 euro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\"